"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Martell.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/30px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/45px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/60px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a></b></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/45px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/60px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Rosby.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Rosby.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e8/House_Rosby.svg/20px-House_Rosby.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e8/House_Rosby.svg/30px-House_Rosby.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e8/House_Rosby.svg/40px-House_Rosby.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rosby\" title=\"House Rosby\">House Rosby</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Martell.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/20px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/30px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/40px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Meria_Martell\" title=\"Meria Martell\">Meria Martell</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Rosby.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Rosby.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e8/House_Rosby.svg/20px-House_Rosby.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e8/House_Rosby.svg/30px-House_Rosby.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e8/House_Rosby.svg/40px-House_Rosby.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Rosby\" title=\"Jon Rosby\">Jon Rosby</a>†</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Lord Jon Rosby<br />Iron Throne garrison</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Defenestration of Sunspear</b> was an event during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a> which took place at <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/5_AC\" title=\"5 AC\">5&#160;AC</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Defenestration_of_Sunspear&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Soon after the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">Targaryens</a> returned to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, the Dornish swarmed from the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear#Shadow_city\" title=\"Sunspear\">shadow city</a> to retake Sunspear. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Rosby\" title=\"Jon Rosby\">Jon Rosby</a>, who had been named <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">Castellan</a> of Sunspear and <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_Sands\" title=\"Warden of the Sands\">Warden of the Sands</a> by King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>, was bound hand and foot, dragged to the top of the Spear Tower and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Defenestration\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Defenestration\">defenestrated</a> from a window by none other than the blind <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Princess</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Meria_Martell\" title=\"Meria Martell\">Meria Martell</a> herself.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon:_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon:_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Defenestration_of_Sunspear&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Dorne: Dorne Against the Dragons.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon:_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon:_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Reign of the Dragon: The Wars of King Aegon I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404021343\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.062 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.208 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 326/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9184/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8673/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1345/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1304/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.130/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.3 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  191.867      1 -total\n 93.36%  179.122      1 Template:Battlebox\n 92.76%  177.980      1 Template:Infobox\n  4.59%    8.810      2 Template:Date\n  3.99%    7.659      2 Template:Ref\n  2.10%    4.022      2 Template:Ref/core\n  1.37%    2.621      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key w